177
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,370
There are 365 days in a year.

178
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,060
There are 24 hours in a day.

179
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:24,120
How could we know

180
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:26,020
